        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 27 at 1:33PM CDT until June 27 at 2:00PM CDT by NWS Lincoln IL</headline>
        <description>At 133 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Westfield, or
near Charleston, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe storm will be near...
Westfield around 140 PM CDT.

Other locations impacted by this severe thunderstorm include Fox
Ridge State Park.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
